            <lg xml:id="TK197">
<l>nayaṉila colliṉuñ colluka cāṉṟōr</l>
<l>payaṉila collāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the wise if they will, speak things without excellence; it will be well for them not to speak useless things.</l>
